  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "フルーツ村の住人となり、40種類のミニゲームをプレイして村を活性化させましょう。村の住人たちと友達になると、店舗を開くこともできます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Fruits-mura no Doubutsu-tachi is a cutesy collection of mini-games and events for one player. You build up your relationship with a group of friends who've come from across the seas to Fruits Village.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "You build up your relationship with a group of friends who've come from across the seas to Fruits Village. To strengthen your relationship, you'll have to win at the over forty mini games included in the game. Friends who've gotten really fond of you will build a home, open stores and help make Fruits Village a fun place for all! How fun can you make Fruits Village before the start of the big festival? All in all, more than 40 mini-games are included.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "2004-10-28",
